Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 6
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Will an ally of Naruto sacrifice his own life to prevent Naruto from risking his own?
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 57
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Negi, the boy wizard, learns he will be teaching English at an all-girls high school in Japan, but he must keep his powers a secret.
Title: NEGIMA! MAGISTER NEGI MAGI, VOL. 35
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO+VAMPIRE: SEASON II, VOL. 9
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Karakura Town hangs in the balance of a fierce battle.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 42
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 43
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.”
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 63
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: 15-year-old Allen Walker roams the earth searching for "Innocence," the material used to create weapons that can destroy demons that this fictional version of 19th century England.
Title: D. GRAY-MAN, VOL. 21
Author: Katsura Hoshino

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry.
Title: BAKUMAN VOL. 12
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 14
Author: Matsuri Hino
